description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 47, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 141, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 5 for East, Box for South, and Leverage for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
